CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 4, 1950, pg. 8, reads: "The Kolesque - This group of lovely young ladies, members of the popular Kolesque Club, surround their calendar for 1950...Kolesque Kalendar for 1950: Feb. - Skate and Dance Party; March - Koronation Ball; May - Balloon Ball; June - Snow Ball (Invitational Formal); August - Kountry Kaboodle; Dec. - A Midnight Masquerade... - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Beatrice Scott (Harris) wearing light colored short sleeved sweater and dark skirt, posed in front of light colored background, in Harris Studio
